Okay, we've got quite the list this time. You ready?

All right, we've got {@LinkCreature:9#810#gula gourmands}, {@LinkCreature:9#910#caiman zealots}, {@LinkCreature:9#440#gula eviscerators}, {@LinkCreature:9#450#gula ragers}, {@LinkCreature:9#1000#Lokian bloodreapers}, {@LinkCreature:9#1100#Lokian bowmasters}, {@LinkCreature:9#1200#Lokian champions}, and {@LinkCreature:9#1300#Lokian bloodragers}. All need killing.

Head over to Noleta when you've finished that up.
Keep this up, and we'll wipe them out soon enough, <PCNAME>.
Have you even started? And if not, why not?
